OL,3,CWoman spends hundreds of pounds at
OL,4,Chotel and then leaves without paying
OL,6,FA woman allegedly racked up nearly
OL,7,F#800 of bills at a Llanelli hotel
OL,8,Fbefore disappearing without paying.
OL,10,FOver a three-night stay at the
OL,11,FDiplomat Hotel, the woman drank at the
OL,12,Fbar and ordered meals to the tune of
OL,13,F#780.
OL,15,FThe management at the hotel say they
OL,16,Fsuspect her booking was made under a
OL,17,Ffalse name.
