OL,6,FPaul Jenkins, the hotel's manager,
OL,7,Fsaid he had been unable to contact the
OL,8,Fwoman and her card declined when the
OL,9,Fhotel tried taking payment. He posted
OL,10,Fon social media in a bid to identify
OL,11,Fher.
OL,13,FMr Jenkins said, "The reception staff
OL,14,Fwould have treated her like any other
OL,15,Fperson checking in... she didn't seem
OL,16,Fany different to anybody else.
