OL,6,F"It's unlikely we're going to get any
OL,7,Fmoney (back). My basic concern is that
OL,8,Fthis goes out so nobody suffers the
OL,9,Fsame thing. We don't get it often but
OL,10,Fit is a revenue loss for the hotel...
OL,11,Fevery day is important for us.
OL,13,F"It's a family-run hotel and outgoings
OL,14,Fare quite a lot. We work hard as a
OL,15,Ffamily and our staff work hard." His
OL,16,Fmessage to the woman who allegedly
OL,17,Fwalked out without paying is: "Just
OL,18,Fpay the bill.
