OL,6,FA Dyfed-Powys Police spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Police received a call on
OL,8,FMonday afternoon, 17th June, reporting
OL,9,Fa woman had stayed at the Diplomat
OL,10,FHotel, Llanelli and left without
OL,11,Fpaying. The woman had stayed at the
OL,12,Fhotel on Monday 10, Tuesday 11 and
OL,13,FWednesday 12 June 2024. Enquiries are
OL,14,Fbeing made to identify the woman."
